        "timestamp": "2019-10-15 13:46:38.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nThis change is to support Service Objects that use the \"object\" valueType. Here I updated service catalog to use \"object\" not \"Object\" as per example in latest TMF 641 / 633 Specs. I also added tests to send Order with ServiceCharacteristic with valueType set to object. For backward compatibility I also allowed sensing serviceCharacteristic as normal, e.g. to support existing use of the Order API from BBS, CCVPN etc use cases. i.e. only those that you the new schemaLocation \"object\" from Service Catalog will notice any change",
        "patchset_number": 2
      },
